  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'Upon arriving, you find the outpost completely deserted.


      The
      body of what appears to be a high ranking officer is hanging from a noose and
      seems badly burned.'
    audioClip: {fileID: 0}
    nextOption: That's not good!
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'The body of the commander was burned with such an intense heat
      that it is nearly made of glass.


      Strangely, nothing around it seems
      to be burnt.'
    audioClip: {fileID: 0}
    nextOption: How Odd
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'Around the outpost, you can spot what appear to be dead guards.


      Go
      investigate and try to figure out what happened.'
    audioClip: {fileID: 0}
    nextOption: I'll go now
